Welcome to the W3C {{ group.name }}!

The following link will lead you to the group page, where 
a lot of information is accessible:

https://www.w3.org/groups/wg/webperf/

In particular, the tools and resources that are
essential in the groups' activities are presented at:

https://www.w3.org/groups/wg/webperf/tools

Please take a few minutes to browse and bookmark this information.

If you have not already done so, link your GitHub account to your W3C account:
  https://www.w3.org/users/myprofile/connectedaccounts

All participants are required to follow the W3C Code of Ethics and Professional Conduct:
  https://www.w3.org/Consortium/cepc/

Should you have any questions on how to get up to speed with the
Group, please get in touch with the Staff Contact or the Chairs
of the group.
